<section class="container">
  <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>

  <div class="faq-list">

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>
        Do I need a partner?
        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
      </summary>
      <p>
        No partner is required! West Coast Swing is a social dance, and we rotate partners frequently.
      </p>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>
        Do I need to know West Coast Swing?
        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
      </summary>
      <p>
        Not at all! We welcome beginners and generally have introductory lessons before dances.
      </p>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>
        What should I wear?
        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
      </summary>
      <p>
        Wear something comfortable you can move in. Smooth-soled shoes are recommended.
      </p>
    </details>

